The reviewer correctly identified that DescendantIds (computed from ALL project items on the backend) may reference items not in the frontend lookup (e.g., done items filtered from the board view). Silent TryGetValue misses would cause progress bars to show incorrect counts. The fix: log warnings for missing descendants so the behavior is observable, and document the contract.

