Every `BlockedIndicator` (one per card) independently subscribes to `DependencyStore.OnChanged`. With 108 cards in the Done column, that is 108 event subscriptions each calling `InvokeAsync(StateHasChanged)` on every dependency change — 108 independent re-render requests.

