### Virtualize without ItemSize (dynamic measurement)

Do NOT use `ItemSize` — Epic/Story/Task cards have different heights (~100-150px), and a fixed `ItemSize` causes scroll jitter as Blazor corrects its estimates. Instead, omit `ItemSize` entirely and let Blazor measure actual card heights dynamically. The slight measurement overhead (~5-10ms) is negligible vs. rendering 108 cards, and we get zero scroll jitter with variable-height cards.

