- Both parameters are `&[WorkItem]` (borrowed). No ownership transfer, no unnecessary clones.
- Hierarchy is computed from `all_project_items`, ensuring ancestors/descendants reference items even if they are filtered out of the response list.
- `unwrap_or_default` returns `(Vec::new(), Vec::new())` if an item is missing from the hierarchy map.
- The `clone()` on ancestor/descendant vecs is necessary because the hierarchy map is borrowed while we iterate.
